summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Securebooking rental agreement app with mocked BankID and Swish integrations. Backend APIs working perfectly, frontend has minor UI state management issue during signing transitions.

ui_bugs.issue: UI state not properly resetting between tenant and landlord signing steps
ui_bugs.description: After tenant completes BankID signing, the component shows 'Signering genomf√∂rd!' (completed) state instead of resetting to allow landlord to start signing. Status badge updates correctly but UI component state is stuck.

integration_issues.issue: Component state management during signer transitions
integration_issues.description: The BankID component doesn't properly reset its internal state when transitioning from tenant to landlord signing, causing UI to show completed state instead of new signing interface.
